// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-6035 — Mass File Rename (apt73)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4f471197-07c2-57a3-bf83-309761107bc1

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
